{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":10101,"text":"(Breathes in)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12384,"text":"(Breathes out)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18014,"text":"So, I didn't always make\nmy living from music."},{"time":21863,"text":"For about the five years after graduating"},{"time":23887,"text":"from an upstanding\nliberal arts university,"},{"time":27016,"text":"this was my day job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29871,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31103,"text":"I was a self-employed living\nstatue called the Eight-Foot Bride,"},{"time":35671,"text":"and I love telling people\nI did this for a job,"},{"time":39411,"text":"because everybody always wants to know,"},{"time":41396,"text":"who are these freaks in real life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43375,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44400,"text":"Hello."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45892,"text":"I painted myself white\none day, stood on a box,"},{"time":49071,"text":"put a hat or a can at my feet,"},{"time":51479,"text":"and when someone came by\nand dropped in money,"},{"time":53830,"text":"I handed them a flower --"},{"time":57911,"text":"and some intense eye contact."},{"time":61987,"text":"And if they didn't take the flower,"},{"time":63711,"text":"I threw in a gesture\nof sadness and longing --"},{"time":67757,"text":"as they walked away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71941,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75645,"text":"So I had the most profound\nencounters with people,"},{"time":79635,"text":"especially lonely people"},{"time":80970,"text":"who looked like they hadn't talked\nto anyone in weeks,"},{"time":84319,"text":"and we would get this beautiful moment\nof prolonged eye contact"},{"time":90312,"text":"being allowed in a city street,"},{"time":92629,"text":"and we would sort of fall\nin love a little bit."},{"time":95941,"text":"And my eyes would say --"},{"time":98433,"text":"\"Thank you."},{"time":100028,"text":"I see you.\""},{"time":101925,"text":"And their eyes would say --"},{"time":105329,"text":"\"Nobody ever sees me."},{"time":107901,"text":"Thank you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":110908,"text":"I would get harassed sometimes."},{"time":112417,"text":"People would yell at me from their cars."},{"time":114505,"text":"\"Get a job!\""},{"time":116147,"text":"(Laughing) And I'd be, like,"},{"time":118211,"text":"\"This is my job.\""},{"time":120041,"text":"But it hurt, because it made me fear"},{"time":123774,"text":"that I was somehow doing\nsomething un-joblike"},{"time":128032,"text":"and unfair, shameful."},{"time":131146,"text":"I had no idea how perfect\na real education I was getting"},{"time":136019,"text":"for the music business on this box."},{"time":138755,"text":"And for the economists out there,"},{"time":140351,"text":"you may be interested to know I actually\nmade a pretty predictable income,"},{"time":143956,"text":"which was shocking to me,\ngiven I had no regular customers,"},{"time":148171,"text":"but pretty much 60 bucks on a Tuesday,\n90 bucks on a Friday."},{"time":151459,"text":"It was consistent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152744,"text":"And meanwhile, I was touring locally\nand playing in nightclubs"},{"time":156228,"text":"with my band, the Dresden Dolls."},{"time":158090,"text":"This was me on piano, a genius drummer."},{"time":160188,"text":"I wrote the songs, and eventually"},{"time":162101,"text":"we started making enough money\nthat I could quit being a statue,"},{"time":166487,"text":"and as we started touring,"},{"time":168748,"text":"I really didn't want to lose this sense"},{"time":171122,"text":"of direct connection with people,\nbecause I loved it."},{"time":173822,"text":"So after all of our shows,\nwe would sign autographs"},{"time":177777,"text":"and hug fans and hang out\nand talk to people,"},{"time":180689,"text":"and we made an art out\nof asking people to help us and join us,"},{"time":186381,"text":"and I would track down\nlocal musicians and artists"},{"time":189527,"text":"and they would set up\noutside of our shows,"},{"time":192719,"text":"and they would pass the hat,"},{"time":194207,"text":"and then they would come in\nand join us onstage,"},{"time":196707,"text":"so we had this rotating smorgasbord\nof weird, random circus guests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200715,"text":"And then Twitter came along,"},{"time":203220,"text":"and made things even more magic,"},{"time":205276,"text":"because I could ask instantly\nfor anything anywhere."},{"time":208035,"text":"So I would need a piano to practice on,"},{"time":210100,"text":"and an hour later I would be\nat a fan's house."},{"time":212393,"text":"This is in London."},{"time":213834,"text":"People would bring home-cooked food to us"},{"time":215938,"text":"all over the world backstage\nand feed us and eat with us."},{"time":218677,"text":"This is in Seattle."},{"time":220083,"text":"Fans who worked in museums and stores"},{"time":223710,"text":"and any kind of public space\nwould wave their hands"},{"time":226917,"text":"if I would decide to do\na last-minute, spontaneous, free gig."},{"time":230181,"text":"This is a library in Auckland."},{"time":233604,"text":"On Saturday I tweeted\nfor this crate and hat,"},{"time":238081,"text":"because I did not want to schlep them\nfrom the East Coast,"},{"time":240864,"text":"and they showed up care of this dude,\nChris, from Newport Beach,"},{"time":243911,"text":"who says hello."},{"time":245644,"text":"I once tweeted, \"Where in Melbourne\ncan I buy a neti pot?\""},{"time":249350,"text":"And a nurse from a hospital drove one"},{"time":251880,"text":"right at that moment to the cafe I was in,"},{"time":254151,"text":"and I bought her a smoothie"},{"time":255619,"text":"and we sat there talking\nabout nursing and death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258183,"text":"And I love this kind of random closeness,"},{"time":261238,"text":"which is lucky, because I do\na lot of couchsurfing."},{"time":265928,"text":"In mansions where everyone\nin my crew gets their own room"},{"time":269042,"text":"but there's no wireless,"},{"time":270319,"text":"and in punk squats,"},{"time":271875,"text":"everyone on the floor\nin one room with no toilets"},{"time":274837,"text":"but with wireless,\nclearly making it the better option."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278654,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280999,"text":"My crew once pulled our van\nup to a really poor Miami neighborhood"},{"time":287089,"text":"and we found out that our couchsurfing\nhost for the night"},{"time":289795,"text":"was an 18-year-old girl,\nstill living at home,"},{"time":292382,"text":"and her family were all undocumented\nimmigrants from Honduras."},{"time":297006,"text":"And that night, her whole family"},{"time":300406,"text":"took the couches and she slept\ntogether with her mom"},{"time":303483,"text":"so that we could take their beds."},{"time":306038,"text":"And I lay there thinking,"},{"time":308879,"text":"these people have so little."},{"time":311673,"text":"Is this fair?"},{"time":313773,"text":"And in the morning,"},{"time":315110,"text":"her mom taught us\nhow to try to make tortillas"},{"time":317457,"text":"and wanted to give me a Bible,"},{"time":319458,"text":"and she took me aside and she said\nto me in her broken English,"},{"time":325051,"text":"\"Your music has helped\nmy daughter so much."},{"time":330584,"text":"Thank you for staying here.\nWe're all so grateful.\""},{"time":333894,"text":"And I thought, this is fair."},{"time":338178,"text":"This is this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341305,"text":"A couple of months later,\nI was in Manhattan,"},{"time":344249,"text":"and I tweeted for a crash pad,\nand at midnight,"},{"time":346537,"text":"I'm on the Lower East Side,"},{"time":348339,"text":"and it occurs to me I've never\nactually done this alone."},{"time":351132,"text":"I've always been with my band or my crew."},{"time":353109,"text":"Is this what stupid people do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":355414,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356945,"text":"Is this how stupid people die?"},{"time":359344,"text":"And before I can change my mind,\nthe door busts open."},{"time":361893,"text":"She's an artist."},{"time":362948,"text":"He's a financial blogger for Reuters,"},{"time":365292,"text":"and they're pouring me a glass of red wine"},{"time":367330,"text":"and offering me a bath,"},{"time":368501,"text":"and I have had thousands of nights\nlike that and like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373810,"text":"So I couchsurf a lot.\nI also crowdsurf a lot."},{"time":377848,"text":"I maintain couchsurfing and crowdsurfing"},{"time":380809,"text":"are basically the same thing."},{"time":383057,"text":"You're falling into the audience"},{"time":385562,"text":"and you're trusting each other."},{"time":387429,"text":"I once asked an opening band of mine"},{"time":389717,"text":"if they wanted to go out\ninto the crowd and pass the hat"},{"time":392408,"text":"to get some extra money,\nsomething that I did a lot."},{"time":395122,"text":"And as usual, the band was psyched,"},{"time":396934,"text":"but there was this one guy in the band"},{"time":399132,"text":"who told me he just couldn't\nbring himself to go out there."},{"time":403014,"text":"It felt too much like begging\nto stand there with the hat."},{"time":407208,"text":"And I recognized his fear"},{"time":410852,"text":"of \"Is this fair?\""},{"time":412965,"text":"and \"Get a job.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":415756,"text":"And meanwhile, my band\nis becoming bigger and bigger."},{"time":418856,"text":"We sign with a major label."},{"time":421011,"text":"And our music is a cross\nbetween punk and cabaret."},{"time":423949,"text":"It's not for everybody."},{"time":425355,"text":"Well, maybe it's for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427806,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429914,"text":"We sign, and there's all this hype\nleading up to our next record."},{"time":433734,"text":"And it comes out and it sells\nabout 25,000 copies"},{"time":437427,"text":"in the first few weeks,"},{"time":438740,"text":"and the label considers this a failure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442708,"text":"I was like, \"25,000, isn't that a lot?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":444621,"text":"They said, \"No, the sales are going down."},{"time":446613,"text":"It's a failure.\""},{"time":447653,"text":"And they walk off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449578,"text":"Right at this same time,\nI'm signing and hugging after a gig,"},{"time":452962,"text":"and a guy comes up to me"},{"time":454753,"text":"and hands me a $10 bill,"},{"time":456955,"text":"and he says,"},{"time":458636,"text":"\"I'm sorry, I burned\nyour CD from a friend.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":461478,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":466319,"text":"\"But I read your blog,\nI know you hate your label."},{"time":468851,"text":"I just want you to have this money.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":471731,"text":"And this starts happening all the time."},{"time":475225,"text":"I become the hat after my own gigs,"},{"time":478690,"text":"but I have to physically stand there\nand take the help from people,"},{"time":481976,"text":"and unlike the guy in the opening band,"},{"time":484185,"text":"I've actually had a lot\nof practice standing there."},{"time":488773,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":490331,"text":"And this is the moment I decide"},{"time":492482,"text":"I'm just going to give away\nmy music for free"},{"time":495374,"text":"online whenever possible,"},{"time":497106,"text":"so it's like Metallica\nover here, Napster, bad;"},{"time":500592,"text":"Amanda Palmer over here,"},{"time":502282,"text":"and I'm going to encourage\ntorrenting, downloading, sharing,"},{"time":505581,"text":"but I'm going to ask for help,"},{"time":507703,"text":"because I saw it work on the street."},{"time":510999,"text":"So I fought my way off my label,\nand for my next project"},{"time":513927,"text":"with my new band,\nthe Grand Theft Orchestra,"},{"time":516631,"text":"I turned to crowdfunding."},{"time":519359,"text":"And I fell into those thousands\nof connections that I'd made,"},{"time":523527,"text":"and I asked my crowd to catch me."},{"time":526792,"text":"And the goal was 100,000 dollars."},{"time":529658,"text":"My fans backed me at nearly 1.2 million,"},{"time":533197,"text":"which was the biggest music\ncrowdfunding project to date."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536103,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540191,"text":"And you can see how many people it is."},{"time":544858,"text":"It's about 25,000 people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548239,"text":"And the media asked,"},{"time":549733,"text":"\"Amanda, the music business is tanking\nand you encourage piracy."},{"time":553211,"text":"How did you make\nall these people pay for music?\""},{"time":555569,"text":"And the real answer is,\nI didn't make them."},{"time":558398,"text":"I asked them."},{"time":560258,"text":"And through the very act of asking people,"},{"time":564120,"text":"I'd connected with them,"},{"time":565836,"text":"and when you connect with them,\npeople want to help you."},{"time":570995,"text":"It's kind of counterintuitive\nfor a lot of artists."},{"time":574765,"text":"They don't want to ask for things."},{"time":576455,"text":"But it's not easy."},{"time":580132,"text":"It's not easy to ask."},{"time":582116,"text":"And a lot of artists have\na problem with this."},{"time":584322,"text":"Asking makes you vulnerable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586613,"text":"And I got a lot of criticism online,"},{"time":591161,"text":"after my Kickstarter went big,"},{"time":592782,"text":"for continuing my crazy\ncrowdsourcing practices,"},{"time":595741,"text":"specifically for asking musicians"},{"time":598622,"text":"who are fans if they wanted\nto join us on stage"},{"time":600995,"text":"for a few songs in exchange\nfor love and tickets and beer,"},{"time":605310,"text":"and this was a doctored image\nthat went up of me on a website."},{"time":610342,"text":"And this hurt in a really familiar way."},{"time":613956,"text":"And people saying,"},{"time":615682,"text":"\"You're not allowed anymore\nto ask for that kind of help,\""},{"time":618735,"text":"really reminded me of the people\nin their cars yelling, \"Get a job.\""},{"time":623849,"text":"Because they weren't\nwith us on the sidewalk,"},{"time":627976,"text":"and they couldn't see the exchange"},{"time":631233,"text":"that was happening\nbetween me and my crowd,"},{"time":633305,"text":"an exchange that was very fair\nto us but alien to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638948,"text":"So this is slightly not safe for work."},{"time":640995,"text":"This is my Kickstarter\nbacker party in Berlin."},{"time":643582,"text":"At the end of the night, I stripped\nand let everyone draw on me."},{"time":646639,"text":"Now let me tell you,\nif you want to experience"},{"time":649656,"text":"the visceral feeling\nof trusting strangers --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":652151,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":653622,"text":"I recommend this,"},{"time":654837,"text":"especially if those strangers\nare drunk German people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658204,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":660139,"text":"This was a ninja\nmaster-level fan connection,"},{"time":663983,"text":"because what I was really saying here was,"},{"time":666503,"text":"I trust you this much."},{"time":669095,"text":"Should I?"},{"time":670984,"text":"Show me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673223,"text":"For most of human history,"},{"time":675259,"text":"musicians, artists, they've been\npart of the community."},{"time":680617,"text":"Connectors and openers,\nnot untouchable stars."},{"time":684834,"text":"Celebrity is about a lot of people\nloving you from a distance,"},{"time":689176,"text":"but the Internet"},{"time":690345,"text":"and the content that we're freely\nable to share on it"},{"time":693970,"text":"are taking us back."},{"time":696744,"text":"It's about a few people\nloving you up close"},{"time":700452,"text":"and about those people being enough."},{"time":705003,"text":"So a lot of people\nare confused by the idea"},{"time":707154,"text":"of no hard sticker price."},{"time":708469,"text":"They see it as an unpredictable risk,\nbut the things I've done,"},{"time":711691,"text":"the Kickstarter, the street, the doorbell,"},{"time":714103,"text":"I don't see these things as risk."},{"time":715957,"text":"I see them as trust."},{"time":718075,"text":"Now, the online tools"},{"time":720093,"text":"to make the exchange as easy\nand as instinctive as the street,"},{"time":724865,"text":"they're getting there."},{"time":726603,"text":"But the perfect tools\naren't going to help us"},{"time":730202,"text":"if we can't face each other"},{"time":732670,"text":"and give and receive fearlessly,"},{"time":735729,"text":"but, more important --"},{"time":738631,"text":"to ask without shame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741965,"text":"My music career has been spent"},{"time":744600,"text":"trying to encounter people on the Internet\nthe way I could on the box."},{"time":750003,"text":"So blogging and tweeting\nnot just about my tour dates"},{"time":753515,"text":"and my new video\nbut about our work and our art"},{"time":757106,"text":"and our fears and our hangovers,"},{"time":760247,"text":"our mistakes,"},{"time":761689,"text":"and we see each other."},{"time":763940,"text":"And I think when we really see each other,"},{"time":767558,"text":"we want to help each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771763,"text":"I think people have been obsessed\nwith the wrong question,"},{"time":774926,"text":"which is, \"How do we make\npeople pay for music?\""},{"time":778822,"text":"What if we started asking,"},{"time":781650,"text":"\"How do we let people pay for music?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":786532,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787700,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}